:INFO
Add a Spigot and Overflow
Drill a hole near the bottom of the barrel for a 3/4-inch brass hose spigot. Use a \
rubber washer and silicone sealant on both sides for a watertight fit. Elevate the \
barrel on cinder blocks or a sturdy wooden platform at least 30 cm off the ground to

